!! Trigger symbols
%^2VAPOC:0 ! second-syllable-vowel apocope
%^DPAL:0   ! depalatalization
%^AUML:0   ! a-umlaut, e.g. 3Sg.Prs or Ill.Sg
%^WG:0     ! weak consonant stem gradation

!! Morpheme boundaries
%> ! Inflectional suffix
%^ ! (exceptional) soft hyphenation point
